          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors* Two methods were used in the cross",
                "section determinations- a standard activation method",
                "for the (p,n),(p,3n),(p,p+n)+(p+d) reaction and",
                "in-beam gamma-ray method in case of the (p,2n)",
                "reaction.",
                "*By authors* Cross section for the (p,n),(p,2n),",
                " (p,3n) and (p,n+p)+(p,d) reactions on Th-232 target",
                "were measured by comparison with the K-shell ionization",
                "cross-section, for proton energy between 6.8 and",
                " 20.2 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
