              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/By authors/ The total cross section have been",
                " expressed as sigma(p,2n)=sigma-84+ delta-sigma'+",
                " +delta-sigma'', where delta-sigma' and delta-sigma''",
                " are correction terms. The correction delta-sigma' is",
                " obtained from the intensity of the 68.5 keV",
                " transition and from the intensity difference of the",
                "  58.6 and 25.6 keV transitions. Delta-sigma'' should",
                " account for the feeding of the ground-and the 9.2 keV",
                "states by transitions from levels higher than 84.2 keV."
